data.text:
Social media celebrity who initially gained attention as the son of soccer player Billy Wingrove. His fame escalated when his family launched his own YouTube channel which has reached more than 2.2 million subscribers.

Before Fame

His parents created his personal Instagram page which has since grown to over 30,000 followers.

Trivia

In March 2019, his family uploaded his first YouTube video titled Learning to Drive My G-Wagon.

Family Life

His father Billy runs the F2Freestylers soccer YouTube channel and his mother's name is Katie. He has an older sister named Amelie who was born in 2009.

Associated With

In an August 2020 video on The Wingrove Family YouTube channel, he was asked questions such as "Who is Boris Johnson?" and "Is Donald Trump a good president?"
